EN: We should encourage children to read more books.
ZH: 这个系列的书籍已经出版了十年。
EN: This series of books has been published for ten years.
ZH: 他有非常丰富的书籍收藏。
EN: He has a very extensive collection of books.
ZH: 这间书店销售各种书籍和杂志。
